Grove Hero "Off The Porch" Interview

Last week we linked back with Memphis native Grove Hero for an exclusive “Off The Porch” interview! During our conversation he talked about his new chain dedicated to Young Dolph, shares some insight about Dolph that the average fan might not know, touring with PRE, Dolph changing his life, his reaction when he heard the news about the shooting, keeping his career going for Dolph, share some of his favorite memories with him, his legacy, still pushing the Paper Route brand, explains why Yo Gotti should of made a post condemning the violence in Memphis, investing into real estate, fixing up houses to let people live in them rent-free, plans to do a Long Live Dolph tour, upcoming starring role in Boosie’s movie, shares some advice for the youth, and much more!
